## Comparison Table

| Property | Full | Complete | Perfect | Balanced | Degenerate |
|----------|------|----------|---------|----------|-----------|
| All internal nodes have 2 children | ✓ | ✗ | ✓ | ✗ | ✗ |
| Last level completely filled | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ | ✗ | ✗ |
| Last level filled left to right | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✗ | ✗ |
| Height | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(n) |
| Search time | O(n) | O(n) | O(n) | O(log n) | O(n) |

